\n<Sister>Everyone has someone they wish to meet again. Living in

\n<Sister>To meet again beyond death. It's something everyone dreams
of and then gives up on. Is this still a difficult concept
for you to grasp?

\n<Rui>But that doesn't mean you can just use people for
experiments as you please! Necromancy isn't such a good
thing! You'll turn into a zombie!

\n<Rui>Necromancy is banned by magical law. Besides, even if they
come back, they'll only be zombies.
1シスター笑い

because it's taboo. Ethics can sometimes cloud our vision.
1シスター笑い2

\n<Sister>Moreover, this town places little value on life. People die
in brawls, drown in alcohol, drugs, hunger, disease... Death
is so commonplace that there's no room to mourn.
